## MapEntry type

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export type MapEntry<T extends ReadonlyMap<unknown, unknown>> =
  T extends ReadonlyMap<infer K, infer V> ? [K, V] : never
```

## Example


```ts
type Foo = Map<number, string>

// Expect: [number, string]
type EntryType = MapEntry<Foo>
```
